Class Algorithm

java.lang.Object
  networks.Algorithm
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AlgorithmCompetitiveLearning, AlgorithmCompetitiveLearningDemo, AlgorithmGrowingCellStructures, AlgorithmGrowingNeuralGas, AlgorithmNeuralGas, AlgorithmSOM
public abstract class Algorithm
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

Title: Competitive Learning

Description: Provides an abstract stub for concrete algorithm classes. The algorithms have a runnable state, and must provide an implementation of the run() and getGraph() methods. In addition, the run() method should make a call to delay() to yield some cpu time.

Copyright: Copyright (c) 2005

Company: University of Hertfordshire

Version:
1.0 Initial Release, 1.1 Added static int for long and short delays for thread yield
Author:
Kevin Doherty (e-mail K.A.J.Doherty@herts.ac.uk)
